                           <locus from="ia">Right flyleaf</locus> watermarked <q xml:lang="en"><watermark><orgName role="ppm">Balston &amp; Co</orgName></watermark></q> of papermaker <persName role="ppm" ref="https://viaf.org/viaf/54948875/" key="person_54948875">William Balston (1759–1849)</persName> at Springfield Mill in <placeName><settlement type="town" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/151287843">Maidstone</settlement>, <settlement type="county" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/148861381">Kent</settlement></placeName> and the left flyleaf bears what appears to be the opposite portion of the same insignia.
                           </support>
                        <extent><measure unit="page" quantity="465">465 pages (ii + 465 + ii)</measure>
