                     </handNote> 
                      <handNote scope="major" script="nasta_liq" medium="ink"><locus from="264" to="465">Pages 264–465:</locus>                           
                         <desc>A comparatively hurried nasta‘liq hand with shikastah ligatures in <material>black </material> with names of poets, Arabic passages, and chapter headings in the margins in red.</desc>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
